---
title: Moroccan-Inspired Shrimp and Veggie Tagine with Couscous
description: This dish is bursting with warming, Moroccan-inspired flavours from juicy apricot to sweet roasted red peppers and aromatic spices. Our recipe uses a simple pot to mimic the steaming and flavour-building power of the original tagine – in a fraction of the time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tajine-de-crevettes-et-de-legumes-a-la-marocaine-a7fdb38d.jpg
